------------------TAG ROUTE------------------

### get all tag
GET {{local}}/tag

### create tag
POST {{local}}/tag
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "coucou",
    "color" : "red"
}

### modify tag
PUT {{local}}/tag/38
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "coucou",
    "color" : "erd"
}   

### delete tag
DELETE {{local}}/tag/10



